text: Ordered takeaway... Understaffed.. takes little time but nice service. Quick cleaning. Neat and clean

Understaffed, so don’t aspect reasonable service from the staffs.
Customer need to asked for tissue papers to clean the able by themselves.
And my girl was so upset that the kids meal was sold out.

Updates after a week:
Kids meal still not available!

Despite its small size, this place is incredibly convenient. With two self-service order kiosks, you can quickly place your order. The food waiting time is impressively fast, and the LCD screens clearly indicate when your food is ready for collection. Don't forget to check for online coupons that can be redeemed at the kiosk – a nice money-saving feature. As for the burgers, they were absolutely awesome; Burger King never disappoints. Recommended!

Not sure if they have a proper system here but the service was extremely quick and the food was well done. I ordered and received it in 1min! True definition of fast food. However, there was no indication of which meal was for whom, needed me to actively look out for my meal!
The burgers were small, we weren't full. And the lettuce in the burger was old and rotten.
